  "title": "Senior Sales Merchandiser",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role:</strong></p><p>We are seeking a dynamic and results-driven <strong>Senior Merchandiser </strong>to join our team in Singapore. You will be responsible for managing\nthe key accounts of Departmental stores. The ideal candidate is independent and able to in charge of instore promotions and\nroadshow events.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>·       Build and maintain strong relationships and manage day-to-day operations of major departmental stores (Takashimaya, Metro, Tangs, OG, Isetan and BHG) <br /><br />-       Plan and support sales activities such as in-store promotions, brand fairs, roadshows, and in-house sales events<br /><br />·       Lead a team of promoters in alignment with company direction, promotional plans and sales objective<br /><br />·       Maximize sales through improved shelving, display, promotions, and new product launches</p><p>·       Strive to achieve monthly sales target</p><p>·       Ensure timely execution of marketing plans with key accounts.</p><p>·       Coordinate closely with internal teams (e.g., operations, logistics, supply chain) to maintain healthy inventory levels</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>·       2-3 years sales experience (Modern trade)</p><p>·       Sales motivated, good communication and negotiation skills</p><p>·       Outgoing and friendly and able to handle multiple client accounts</p><p>·       Organized, detail-oriented, and able to multitask in a fast-paced\nenvironment</p><p>·      Work independently and as part of a team in a fast-paced environment </p><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li>Competitive salary and performance bonus</li><li>Opportunities for professional growth and training</li><li>Dynamic and collaborative work culture</li><li>Staff discounts and exclusive perks</li></ul>",
